                           as vendor/glfw)

See each vendor subdirectory for upstream LICENSE files or
https://github.com/KhronosGroup/Vulkan-Headers ,
https://github.com/GPUOpen-LibrariesAndSDKs/VulkanMemoryAllocator ,
